vlc (2.2.6-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/upstream: Add DEP-12 metadata.
  * debian/control:
    - Restrict Recommends on vlc-plugin-samba to linux-any kfreebsd-any.
    - Switch to timgm6mb-soundfont. (Closes: #870790)
    - Bump Standards-Version.
