  * Use DEB_HOST_ARCH instead of DEB_BUILD_ARCH in rules.
  * Use objdump -x instead of ldd to check for links on libX11 as ldd might
    resolve libvlc to the system's version if the system has libvlc installed;
    closes: #495730.

