  * debian/patches/021_x264_powerpc.diff:
    + Patch from upstream to fix FTBFS on PowerPC (Closes: #411438).
  * debian/rules:
    + Fix a kFreeBSD FTBFS, courtesy of Petr Salinger (Closes: #399713).

